To receive a free ticket to the event (unless they are willing to pay for a VIP ticket) spectators had to perform a series of tasks, or "actions", such as volunteering, sending an e-mail to a world leader, a telephone call or any other significant ways that contribute to increasing awareness of the goal of ending poverty.
