Global Citizen states that since 2011, it has recorded more than 19 million "actions" of its supporters who have exerted pressure to achieve a number of different objectives.
These actions, according to the organization, contributed to the announcement by world leaders of commitments and policies valued at more than $37 billion, which will affect the lives of more than 2.25 billion people by 2030.
In early 2018, the group quoted 390 commitments and announcements arising from its actions, with at least $10 billion in respect of the same being already disbursed or raised.
The group estimates that the funds obtained have so far had a direct impact on almost 649 million people scattered around the world.
